22 Apr 2026 20:57:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>1994年印第安人球场旧照</title><link>https://some.pics/69e9348d260df</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天又扫描了几张底片。这是我的朋友凯文和我在雅各布斯球场（现进步球场）的合影。这张照片拍摄于1994年4月15日至17日的某个周末，当时克利夫兰印第安人队主场迎战堪萨斯城皇家队，进行三场系列赛。印第安人队输了，但我们依然玩得很开心。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two men posing together in  the stands at Jacobs Field. The man on the left wears glasses and a red and blue retro-style Cleveland Indians jersey, while the man on the right wears glasses and a denim jacket. The man on the right is holding up a white container above their heads. Both are smiling at the camera." height="4920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69e9348d260df.jpg" width="3280"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:50:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>光影交错</title><link>https://some.pics/69e91b1993830</link><description>&lt;p&gt;投下阴影。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A gardening device and blackberry branches leaving strong shadows on a white wall." height="4494" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69e91b1993830.jpg" width="2529"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 19:01:48 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>